name: REI_ART_PROCS
description: The REI_ART_PROCS table contains information about the procedures needed for the assisted reproductive technology (ART) treatment type, which could be egg retrieval or embryo transfer.

columns.name: CYCLE_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier for the fertility treatment cycle record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: PROCS_C_NAME
columns.description: The procedures needed for the assisted reproductive technology (ART) treatment type, which include egg retrieval or embryo transfer.
